<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tʿạl</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yswʿ rby ṣạnʿ ạlkẖlạṣ yqwl ạ̉nạ hw ạlbạb tʿạl
 ạ̉dkẖl wậmn bh bạ̹kẖlạṣ tgẖfr kẖṭạyạk wạlrḍạ tnạl
 ln tkẖsr bl trbḥ tʿạl ạlmʿṭy bskẖạ yʿṭyk tʿạl
 ln ttʿb bl trtạḥ tʿạl mryḥ ạltʿạby̱ ynạdyk
 ln tʿṭsẖ bl trwy̱ tʿạl mrwy ạlʿṭạsẖ yrwyk
 ln tḥzn bl tfrḥ tʿạl ln tndm bl tnʿm tʿạl
 ln tjwʿ bl tsẖbʿ tʿạl ln tmwt bl tḥyạ tʿạl
 tʿạl ạ̹lyh fy ạlḥạl</lyrics>
<author>klwdyt jrjwrẗ, dạnyạl ạlḥạj</author>
